  pi:algorithmDoc   "Performance spectrum — segments all arc traversals in the DFG by time, producing a time-sliced frequency matrix for flow rate visualisation." ;
  pi:citation       "Denisov, V., Fahland, D., & van der Aalst, W.M.P. (2018). Unbiased description of processes performance from event data. BPM 2018, LNCS 11080. Springer." ;
